==评价==
作爲在日本國内外其中一部最著名的動漫作品，《進擊的巨人》曾罕見地獲得了日本政府的官方評價。在2021年4月漫畫最終回發售后，日本[[内閣官房長官|内閣官房長官]][[加藤勝信|加藤勝信]]被記者問及有關感想時表示「《進擊的巨人》是在全世界屢破紀錄的大人氣作品」，並同時表示「以《進擊的巨人》爲代表的日本動漫是我國值得驕傲的文化」、「政府今後也會繼續在知財等方面對動漫產業加强支援」<ref>{{cite news |title=加藤官房長官、進撃の巨人「私自身も単行本で読んでいる」人気漫画が完結（日刊スポーツ） |url=https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/d71828aa330fe46b64a7c6b03a26f29caa6e710b |accessdate=2021-04-09 |work=Yahoo!ニュース |date=2021-04-09 |language=ja |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412185537/https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/d71828aa330fe46b64a7c6b03a26f29caa6e710b |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《進擊的巨人》贏得了2011年的[[講談社漫畫賞|講談社漫畫賞]]少年部門<ref>{{cite web|url=http://corp.kodansha.co.jp/award/archive/manga.html|title=講談社漫画賞 (過去の受賞者一覧)|trans_title=Kodansha Manga Award (list of past winners)|language=ja|publisher=[[講談社|講談社]]|accessdate=April 10, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6H8qYZXFY?url=http://corp.kodansha.co.jp/award/archive/manga.html|archivedate=2013-06-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-05-12/march-comes-in-like-a-lion-space-bros-win-kodansha-manga-awards|title=''March comes in like a lion'', ''Space Bros.'' Win Kodansha Manga Awards|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=May 12, 2011|accessdate=April 10, 2013|archive-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517062850/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-05-12/march-comes-in-like-a-lion-space-bros-win-kodansha-manga-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>，被提名第四屆[[漫畫大獎|漫畫大獎]]、第十六屆及第十八屆[[手塚治虫文化獎|手塚治虫文化獎]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-01-16/13-titles-nominated-for-4th-manga-taisho-awards |title=13 Titles Nominated for 4th Manga Taisho Awards |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |date=January 16, 2011 |accessdate=October 30, 2013 |archive-date=2019-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508225817/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-01-16/13-titles-nominated-for-4th-manga-taisho-awards |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-02-20/16th-tezuka-osamu-cultural-prize-nominees-announced |title=16th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize Nominees Announced |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |date=February 10, 2012 |accessdate=October 30, 2013 |archive-date=2013-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130825095221/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-02-20/16th-tezuka-osamu-cultural-prize-nominees-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-03-09/18th-tezuka-osamu-cultural-prize-nominees-announced |title=18th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize Nominees Announced |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |date=March 9, 2014 |accessdate=March 9, 2014 |archive-date=2014-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309200013/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-03-09/18th-tezuka-osamu-cultural-prize-nominees-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年[[全國書店店員推薦漫畫|全國書店店員推薦漫畫]]排行第一。在《[[這本漫畫真厲害！|這本漫畫真厲害！]]》調查裡，《進擊的巨人》被選為2011年第1佳、2012年第8佳、2013第14佳、2014第6佳的男性向漫畫作品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-12-08/top-manga-ranked-by-kono-manga-ga-sugoi-2012-voters |title=Top Manga Ranked by Kono Manga ga Sugoi 2012 Voters |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |date=December 8, 2011 |accessdate=October 30, 2013 |archive-date=2014-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104182338/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-12-08/top-manga-ranked-by-kono-manga-ga-sugoi-2012-voters |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-12-09/top-manga-ranked-by-kono-manga-ga-sugoi-2014-voters|title=Top Manga Ranked by Kono Manga ga Sugoi 2014 Voters|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=December 9, 2013|accessdate=December 11, 2013|archive-date=2014-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508113757/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-12-09/top-manga-ranked-by-kono-manga-ga-sugoi-2014-voters|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2015年[[讀賣新聞|讀賣新聞]]社主辦的[[SUGOI_JAPAN_Award|SUGOI JAPAN Award]]「最想向海外介紹的[[日本流行文化|日本流行文化]]」大獎中，《進擊的巨人》列為熱門漫畫部門的第一名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2015-03-12/yomiuri-shimbun-sugoi-japan-awards-winners-announced/.85910|title=Yomiuri Shimbun's 'Sugoi Japan Awards' Winners Announced|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115202340/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2015-03-12/yomiuri-shimbun-sugoi-japan-awards-winners-announced/.85910|dead-url=no}}</ref>。單是在2013年裡，《進擊的巨人》漫畫銷售量就達1593萬3801冊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-12-01/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series/2013 |title=Top-Selling Manga in Japan by Series: 2013 |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |date=December 1, 2013 |accessdate=December 1, 2013 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202043338/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-12-01/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series/2013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。依據[[Oricon公信榜|Oricon公信榜]]，至2014年4月為止，《進擊的巨人》已賣出三千萬冊<ref name="sold sales">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-04-23/attack-on-titan-manga-sells-over-30-million|title=Attack on Titan Manga Sells Over 30 Million|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=April 23, 2014|accessdate=April 25, 2014|archive-date=2014-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425075730/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-04-23/attack-on-titan-manga-sells-over-30-million|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2014年上半年，它擊敗了盤踞在榜首長達五年之久的《[[ONE_PIECE|-{zh-tw:航海王;zh-cn:航海王;zh-hk:ONE PIECE;zh-sg:海賊王;}-]]》、成為該期間最受歡迎的作品。諫山對此感到驚訝並感謝讀者愛戴。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-06-01/attack-on-titan-manga-tops-one-piece-in-half-year-sales/.75118|title=Attack on Titan Manga Tops One Piece in Half-Year Sales|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|accessdate=June 15, 2014|archive-date=2014-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140622215713/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-06-01/attack-on-titan-manga-tops-one-piece-in-half-year-sales/.75118|dead-url=no}}</ref>
至年底結算時，它是該年度第二暢銷的漫畫，共賣出1172萬8368冊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2014/11/30-1/one-piece-tops-2014-manga-sales-in-japan-again|title=Crunchyroll|work=Crunchyroll|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2015-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219062905/http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2014/11/30-1/one-piece-tops-2014-manga-sales-in-japan-again|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而在2015年的單年銷售量為877萬8048冊，排行第三名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2015-11-29/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series-2015/.95913|title=Top-Selling Manga in Japan by Series: 2015|author=|date=|work=Anime News Network|accessdate=April 17, 2016|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504033522/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2015-11-29/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series-2015/.95913|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2016年的銷售量時654萬4081冊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-11-30/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series-2016/.109352|title=Top-Selling Manga in Japan by Series: 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2016-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221103619/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-11-30/top-selling-manga-in-japan-by-series-2016/.109352|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年時，《進擊的巨人》讓過去十八年來在[[銷售收入|銷售收入]]持續下滑的漫畫出版商講談社的年度銷售收入獲得增長<ref name="Circulation">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-03-10/attack-on-titan-manga-has-31-million-in-circulation|title=Attack on Titan Manga Has 31 Million in Circulation|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=March 10, 2014|accessdate=March 11, 2014|archive-date=2014-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707041245/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-03-10/attack-on-titan-manga-has-31-million-in-circulation|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而它的動畫也被認為推動了漫畫的銷量，[[每日新聞|每日新聞]]更將之譽為「十年一遇」。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-06-03/attack-on-titan-manga-prints-8.7-million-more-after-anime| title=Attack on Titan Manga Prints 8.7 Million More After Anime| date=June 3, 2013| publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]| accessdate=June 4, 2013| archive-date=2018-12-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206122857/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-06-03/attack-on-titan-manga-prints-8.7-million-more-after-anime| dead-url=no}}</ref>

許多評論認為《進擊的巨人》反映了「當今社會中青年人所感受到的絕望」<ref name="amateur art">{{cite web | author1=Ohara, Atsuhi | author2=Yamane, Yukiko | url=http://ajw.asahi.com/article/cool_japan/culture/AJ201308170034 | title=Boosted by anime version, 'Attack on Titan' manga sales top 22 million | date=August 17, 2013 | publisher=[[Asahi_Shimbun|Asahi Shimbun]] | accessdate=November 1, 2013 | archive-date=2013-08-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822093832/http://ajw.asahi.com/article/cool_japan/culture/AJ201308170034 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。作家山脇稱之為「以即將[[成年禮|成年]]的男女們為中心所進行的故事」，每集都會有一些新的謎團。漫畫評論家{{link-ja|吳智英|呉智英}}表示正是這些奧秘擴大了讀者的期待。某些評論家認為漫畫的畫工很粗陋，而諫山也自認自己的畫功是「業餘的」。不過評論家也認為，經過多年連載洗禮後，畫工持續地在改善。而吳智英則認為，如果畫風被「精煉」了，就無法傳達出該作品裡一個關鍵特色：「怪誕」<ref name="amateur art"/>。在作家{{link-en|傑森·湯普森 (作家)|Jason Thompson (writer)|傑森·湯普森}}對作品的短評裡，指出角色輕易地獲取「能力提升」的管道導致了劇情的曲折，但結論是這些曲折的情節和末日題材是「十分傑出，不容錯過」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/house-of-1000-manga/2013-11-14 |title=House of 1000 Manga – Crunchyroll Manga |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |date=November 14, 2013 |accessdate=February 1, 2014 |archive-date=2013-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131222002301/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/house-of-1000-manga/2013-11-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

動畫在日本取得佳績，九卷BD/DVD的平均銷售量為5萬2067份，截至2016年8月，總銷量達46萬8603張<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.someanithing.com/1|title=2000–Present, Average Sales of 10,000 or More|work=someanithing.com|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2015-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109063142/http://www.someanithing.com/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它不但是2013年日本電視動畫裡銷量中最好的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/12/26/top-funimation-streaming-shows-of-2014/|title=Top FUNimation Streaming Shows of 2014|work=funimation.com|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2015-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910145131/http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/12/26/top-funimation-streaming-shows-of-2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是2014年[[Funimation|Funimation]]上播放率最高的動畫<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/12/29/top-ten-fan-favorite-funimation-home-video-releases-of-2014/|title=Top Ten Fan Favorite FUNimation Home Video Releases of 2014|work=funimation.com|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2015-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150909202222/http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/12/29/top-ten-fan-favorite-funimation-home-video-releases-of-2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在「[[Newtype_(雜誌)|Newtype]]動畫獎」中，《進擊的巨人》動畫贏得了六項殊榮，包括最佳導演、最佳劇本、最佳配樂、最佳主題曲、最佳女性角色和年度總冠軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-10-13/attack-on-titan-wins-top-prizes-in-newtype-anime-awards |title=Attack on Titan Wins Top Prizes in Newtype Anime Awards – News |publisher=Anime News Network |date=October 13, 2013 |accessdate=October 14, 2013 |archive-date=2015-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121103813/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-10-13/attack-on-titan-wins-top-prizes-in-newtype-anime-awards |dead-url=no }}</ref>，此外還贏得2013年[[神戶動畫獎|神戶動畫獎]]最佳電視動畫獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ajw.asahi.com/article/cool_japan/movies/AJ201312210038 |title='Attack on Titan,' 'Garden of Words' take top honors at Kobe anime awards |publisher=[[Asahi_Shimbun|Asahi Shimbun]] |date=December 21, 2013 |accessdate=February 1, 2014 |archive-date=2019-05-26 |archive-url=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20190526222316/http://ajw.asahi.com/article/cool_japan/movies/AJ201312210038 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2014年[[東京動畫獎|東京動畫獎]]年度最佳動畫部門電視部門大獎、最佳導演、最佳劇本、最佳音樂獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://animefestival.jp/en/post/259/|title=Announcement of The Tokyo Anime Award Festival 2014 Anime Of The Year Winning Programs And Winners. – TOKYO ANIME AWARD FESTIVAL 2016 – 東京アニメアワードフェスティバル2016|work=TOKYO ANIME AWARD FESTIVAL 2016 – 東京アニメアワードフェスティバル2016|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2015-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526044423/http://animefestival.jp/en/post/259/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；2013年時，贏得日本第十九屆數位媒體年度協會大獎的年度數位內容獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-03-18/attack-on-titan-wins-digital-contents-of-the-year-award|title=Attack on Titan Wins Digital Contents of the Year Award|work=Anime News Network|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2015-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819224659/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-03-18/attack-on-titan-wins-digital-contents-of-the-year-award|dead-url=no}}</ref>；動畫新聞網的 Carl Kimlinger表示，動畫改編的前兩集極其關鍵，他讚揚這個作品「帶來了如同{{link-en|Fee-fi-fo-fum|Fee-fi-fo-fum}}的恐怖」，不過對後續的內容表示「不是很好的表現」。他批判荒木的做法，表示他「明顯企圖使人感到巨人的強大與令人不安感，但只是透過了粗暴而不愉快的方式」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/carl | title=The Spring 2013 Anime Preview Guide | author=Kimlinger, Carl | date=April 4, 2013 | publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] | accessdate=March 18, 2013 | archive-date=2019-04-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423052003/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/carl | dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一方面，動畫新聞網的其它評論員對這部作品表示讚賞，Rebecca Silverman認為「它的視覺效果華麗且令人震撼，表現出哥德小說家[[安·拉德克利夫|安·拉德克利夫]]描述的，恐怖與恐怖的絕佳組合：一個是物理上的、讓人想要逃離；一個是精神上的，讓你想要知道接下來的發展」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/rebecca | title=The Spring 2013 Anime Preview Guide | author=Silverman, Rebecca | date=April 3, 2013 | publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] | accessdate=March 18, 2013 | archive-date=2019-04-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424081218/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/rebecca | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

有些評論對故事的末日題材十分讚揚。Carlo Santos在只看了動畫的第一集後，便認為《進擊的巨人》是死亡與毀滅的傑作，指出它「接近完美無缺」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/carlo | title=The Spring 2013 Anime Preview Guide | author=Santos, Carlo | date=April 4, 2013 | publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] | accessdate=March 18, 2013 | archive-date=2019-03-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327112131/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/carlo | dead-url=no }}</ref>；而動畫新聞網的 Theron Martin的評價是「強而有力的第一集」，同時讚揚其配樂，並將之與《[[獵魔戰記|獵魔戰記]]》互相比較。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/theron | title=The Spring 2013 Anime Preview Guide | author=Martin, Theron | date=April 3, 2013 | publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] | accessdate=March 18, 2013 | archive-date=2019-04-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421094624/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/preview-guide/2013/the-spring-anime/theron | dead-url=no }}</ref>

漫畫於2021年4月9日完結，大結局的评价好壞參半。<ref>{{Cite web |title=無法接受《進擊的巨人》結局！海外粉絲連署請求重畫 |url=https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-13/562656 |accessdate=2021-04-21 |date=2021-04-13 |work=新頭殼 Newtalk |language=zh-TW |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423200540/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-13/562656 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=《進擊的巨人》結局是爛尾還是神作被吵翻，為什麼越是大作結局越無法讓人滿意？ |url=https://www.techbang.com/posts/86028-is-the-end-of-the-giant-in-attack-a-bad-tail-or-a-work-of-god |accessdate=2021-04-21 |date=2021-04-17 |work=T客邦 |language=zh-tw |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423200518/https://www.techbang.com/posts/86028-is-the-end-of-the-giant-in-attack-a-bad-tail-or-a-work-of-god |dead-url=no }}</ref>也有中國網友翻出谏山创过往的访谈、社交媒体的发言、及对作品设定的分析，主观认为谏山创有蔑视读者，及倾向认同[[右翼|右翼]]和[[日本军国主义|日本军国主义]]的观点<ref>{{Cite web |title=日本华媒：日本右翼污染动漫 惹恼亚洲粉丝-中新网 |url=http://www.chinanews.com/hb/2014/05-23/6205497.shtml |accessdate=2021-04-21 |work=www.chinanews.com |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423200636/http://www.chinanews.com/hb/2014/05-23/6205497.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=破「牆」而出：《進擊的巨人》風靡全球 |url=https://ctee.com.tw/bookstore/magazine/439315.html |accessdate=2021-04-21 |date=2021-04-01 |work=工商時報 |language=zh-TW |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423200528/https://ctee.com.tw/bookstore/magazine/439315.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

